    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You must have a token on the scene to use this spell (Warpgate mutation limitation).</p><p>You must have an actor called \"CPR - Skeleton\" and \"CPR - Zombie\" in the sidebar.</p><p>After casting this spell a new feature called \"Animate Dead - Move\" will be available in your features.</p><p>If you use \"Tidy 5e Sheet\" it will automatically be favorited.</p><p>If you use \"Custom Character Sheet Sections\" it will be in it's own section called \"Spell Features.\"</p><p>You can cast this spell again to animate more undead without reverting spawned creatures.</p><p><em>This spell is safe to be renamed.</em></p>",
